additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Ingredients: Dairy ingredients (reconstituted skim milk and/or reconstituted buttermilk, butter oil (milk), whole milk powder, cream (milk), sugar, cocoa components (10%^)(cocoa mass, cocoa butter), almond, glucose, vegetable oil, emulsifiers (E471, soy lecithin, sunflower lecithin), stabilisers (E412, E410, E407), natural vanilla, flavours, colour (E160b). Contains milk, almond, soy. May contain wheat, gluten, peanut, other tree nuts.
